# Update AI Providers & Local AI Bootstrapping

The goal is to update the application's AI provider configuration with new Azure cloud endpoints, integrate the **Foundry Local** on-device inference server, and ensure that local AI providers (Ollama and Foundry Local) are automatically started and configured during the application's bootstrap process. This ensures a seamless developer experience and robust local-first AI capabilities.

